title: The Evolution of Jenna Marbles - Jenna Marbles' Story (Jenna Mourey)

media:group.media:title: The Evolution of Jenna Marbles - Jenna Marbles' Story (Jenna Mourey)
media:group.media:description:
Few creators could match Jenna Marbles dedication to their fans. From her earliest phases on YouTube to her last few videos she always seemed to act in their best interest. But no one could see the hidden strain of being pressured to maintain such a presence online. While many argue as to while she left, one thing that stands true is that she left on her terms.
